Optimized_Coin_Change(coins, amount)

1.  Create an array DP of size (amount + 1)
2.  Initialize DP[0] = 0
3.  Fill all other DP entries with Infinity
4.  
5.  FOR i FROM 1 TO amount DO:
6.      FOR each coin in coins DO:
7.          IF coin <= i THEN
8.              // استخدم النتيجة المخزنة مسبقاً للمبلغ المتبقي
9.              DP[i] = MIN(DP[i], DP[i - coin] + 1)
10. 
11. IF DP[amount] == Infinity THEN
12.     RETURN -1
13. ELSE
14.     RETURN DP[amount]
